                The goal of the program is to increase graduation rates; transition students into Post-Secondary education and/or work/vocation; and improve parenting skills, 
                creating the overarching goal to decrease child abuse and maltreatment by assisting students in developing the emotional and environmental growth needed to graduate and successfully transition into adulthood.
